🎙️ AI Voice Booking Agent (AI Receptionist)

An autonomous AI-powered voice & text assistant for real-time appointment scheduling, rescheduling, and intelligent customer interaction.

🚀 Overview

The AI Voice Booking Agent is an intelligent AI receptionist designed to automate appointment management and customer inquiries through natural voice and text conversations.

It supports multilingual conversations (Hindi, English, Hinglish), integrates with Google Calendar for real-time scheduling, and uses a FAISS-based RAG pipeline to handle business-related queries with contextual accuracy.

This system simulates a production-ready AI receptionist capable of handling real-world business workflows autonomously.

